":"https://in.marketscreener.com/news/aditya-birla-fashion-appoints-nikhil-modha-as-cfo-designate-effective-april-1-2026-ce7e5edddc81f226","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-24T00:00:00","source":"MarketScreener India"},{"id":"482640","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion and Retail Ltd (ABFRL) reported Q3 FY26 revenue growth of 8% YoY to INR 2,374 crore, with EBITDA margins improving to 15.6% from 14.9% YoY.\nPantaloons showed a 3% LTL growth adjusted for festive/EOSS shifts, while ethnic business expanded 20% YoY with margins at 22.7%. Losses narrowed to INR 115 crore normalized.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion and Retail Ltd (ABFRL) reported Q3 FY26 revenue growth of 8% YoY to INR 2,374 crore, with EBITDA margins improving to 15.6% from 14.9% YoY.\nPantaloons showed a 3% LTL growth adjusted for festive/EOSS shifts, while ethnic business expanded 20% YoY with margins at 22.7%. Losses narrowed to INR 115 crore normalized.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=f409de30-fb04-44d8-9dad-9deb9933f8a6.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-10T14:58:57","source":"BSE"},{"id":"478871","title":"TCNS margins rose 500 bps due to better products, retail execution.\nYTD pre-Ind AS losses dropped 50%, aiming for medium-term double-digit margins.","summary":"TCNS margins rose 500 bps due to better products, retail execution.\nYTD pre-Ind AS losses dropped 50%, aiming for medium-term double-digit margins.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T08:53:24","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"478872","title":"ABFRL expects profitability from next year; TMRW targets break-even by FY29.\nGaleries Lafayette projects INR 150-200 Cr revenue with 20% profitability over time.","summary":"ABFRL expects profitability from next year; TMRW targets break-even by FY29.\nGaleries Lafayette projects INR 150-200 Cr revenue with 20% profitability over time.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T08:53:17","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"478873","title":"ABFRL's Pantaloon targets mid-high single-digit L2L growth, double-digit overall growth.\nTCNS plans 50-60 new stores, targeting double-digit growth; OWNED aims for 40-50 stores by FY '29.","summary":"ABFRL's Pantaloon targets mid-high single-digit L2L growth, double-digit overall growth.\nTCNS plans 50-60 new stores, targeting double-digit growth; OWNED aims for 40-50 stores by FY '29.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T08:53:06","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"474117","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion and Retail (ABFRL) approved the merger of two wholly-owned subsidiaries, Jaypore and TG Apparel & Decor.\nThe merger aims for operational simplification, cost reduction, and enhanced financial flexibility without altering ABFRL's shareholding.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion and Retail (ABFRL) approved the merger of two wholly-owned subsidiaries, Jaypore and TG Apparel & Decor.\nThe merger aims for operational simplification, cost reduction, and enhanced financial flexibility without altering ABFRL's shareholding.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=be7f0906-2517-42c3-abf5-90d8fc86e917.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-05T19:01:01","source":"BSE"},{"id":"474113","title":"ABFRL reported Q3 net loss of ₹152.2 crore, wider than ₹51.3 crore YoY; revenue grew 7.9% to ₹2,373.6 crore.\nEBITDA rose 2.4% to ₹308.6 crore; EBITDA margin declined to 13% from 13.7%. Shares ended 3% higher but fell 6% YTD.","summary":"ABFRL reported Q3 net loss of ₹152.2 crore, wider than ₹51.3 crore YoY; revenue grew 7.9% to ₹2,373.6 crore.\nEBITDA rose 2.4% to ₹308.6 crore; EBITDA margin declined to 13% from 13.7%. Shares ended 3% higher but fell 6% YTD.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/earnings/abfrls-sales-grow-but-losses-deepen-in-q3-even-as-stock-ends-higher-ws-l-19843428.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-05T18:53:28","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"473928","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion's Q3 net loss widened to ₹1.5B from ₹513M YoY.\nRevenue increased to 